**balthisar.com** wants you to be a happy user and so if you have questions,
bug reports, feature suggestions, and so on, then we want to hear from you!

Although you’re always welcome to email us at
[balthisar@balthisar.com](balthisar@balthisar.com) or communicate with us at
[Twitter](https://twitter.com/balthisar_com), may we suggest you also consider
the following options?

- Ensure that you are using the most up-to-date version of _Balthisar Tidy_.
  <% if target_feature?(:feature_sparkle) %>
  Use **Check for Updates…** in the **Balthisar Tidy** main menu. You may also
  consider enabling automatic update checking in **Preferences**.
  <% else %>
  Check the **App Store** to ensure that there are no pending updates awaiting
  your approval. The **App Store** can be setup to download all updates
  automatically.
  <% end %>

- Check _Balthisar Tidy_’s [FAQs](http://www.balthisar.com/software/tidy/faq/).

- Have a look at _Balthisar Tidy_’s [support page](http://www.balthisar.com/software/tidy/support/)
  which always has up-to-date support information.

- Visit our bug tracker and feature request issues list at [github](https://github.com/balthisar/tidy/issues).
  This system will make it easy for you to share your problems with other users
  and provide up-to-the-date information about the status of your requests.
  
